yboard or Timeline view and add audio, transitions and minor effects.","You can choose to have the software automatically chapter your video, or you can add chapters yourself. However, we found that the automatic chaptering feature really doesn&#39;t work well, and we had to go into the Set Chapters tab and create our own chapters anyway.","ShowBiz DVD includes a selection of themed templates. You can also import your own backgrounds and save modified versions of the templates.","ShowBiz DVD only gives you moderate control over the layout of the DVD menus and the way thumbnails are displayed. If there is more than one chapter to your video, the software defaults the thumbnails as the next menu screen. You have to manually set the thumbnail as a picture in the Set Chapters tab.","Additionally, ShowBiz DVD includes a number of minor video-editing features such as the ability to add text to your videos, control the brightness and saturation, adjust scene transitions and even enhance the volume.","Although ShowBiz DVD can capture video from your recording device, it can&#39;t import files directly from a camcorder or optical media. It has to rip your video to the hard drive and then import them from the hard drive. We really like this DVD maker&#39;s ability to capture video from a VHS tape and TV tuner. You can also use the DVD creation software to put together a slideshow with music.","ShowBiz DVD also includes a built-in DVD burner, a label maker and a playback feature that lets you check the menus before you burn a DVD."]},"id":"41c62375-e8fa-446a-b499-cf5473aabafa","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"6fa38be4-11ff-4865-ac54-ce007f9410dd","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["ArcSoft&#39;s ShowBiz DVD isn&#39;t awful DVD authoring software. With a little practice, you can use it to chapter and author your home movies onto navigation-based DVDs. Although ShowBiz DVD is easier to use than some of the other DVD authoring software we reviewed, its inconsistent output quality keeps it from occupying one of the top spots on our lineup."]},"id":"abe62788-2d29-4fad-9927-8bbeda9beb81","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_2678","url":"/showbiz-dvd-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"j-d-chadwick","url":"/author/j-d-chadwick","dateCreated":"2019-04-05T12:55:59Z","name":"J.D. Chadwick","dateModified":"2019-04-05T12:55:59Z","id":"Q2hDFnLxcyQrSWYJF8ZLKH","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2008-10-29T21:34:53Z","datePublished":"2008-10-29T21:34:53Z","name":"ShowBiz DVD","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"rating":52,"verdict":"The inconsistent output is a big showstopper despite all the editing features.","pros":["This application has more editing features than many other products available."],"cons":["The DVDs we created with ShowBiz DVD were inconsistent when we played them back."]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","language":"en","dateModified":"1970-01-01T00:00:00Z","id":"jdTmWnmkx2ZDESdygerQPT","meta":{"title":"ShowBiz DVD Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"Do you want easy-to-use DVD authoring software to use at home? Read our review of ShowBiz DVD to learn about the many features it has to offer."},"products":[{"slug":"showbiz-dvd","url":"/product/showbiz-dvd","dateCreated":"2019-04-05T14:05:50Z","name":"ShowBiz DVD","dateModified":"2019-04-05T14:05:50Z","id":"yREawwbUzH54Bfba6xgPCj","dateImported":"2019-04-05T12:55:59Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-05T14:05:50Z","type":"review"